Price OverviewPrice Detail

Price Overview chart shows development of price over time
  • How often is this game on sale? Are deals getting better?
  • How quickly did it reach current historical low?
  • Is historical low being repeated?
  • Is the regular price of the game dropping?
  • Do all stores drop price?
Price Detail chart shows a per-store view of price history
  • When and how good deals did a store have?
  • Do all stores have deals at the same time?
  • How much prices differ between stores?
  • Are there any differences between sale frequency?
\r\n

Cut OverviewSavings

Cut Overview chart shows development of price cuts over time
  • How often is this game on sale? What is the deals cut?
  • How often are deals repeated?
  • How quickly did price cuts reached current level?
Savings chart shows absolute value of price cut
If regular price drops, same price cut won't mean same savings
\r\n

Sales DistributionSales Duration

Sales distribution chart can tell you when there usually is a sale during a year
  • When are deals more frequent?
  • Are deals with higher cut more frequent during certain time of year?
Note that frequency is aggregate over all historical data and all selected stores
Sales duration chart may tell you how long a sale usually lasts
  • Do deals with smaller cut last longer? By how much?
  • What is a median duration of a sale?
  • How many times was a game on sale with a price cut?
Note that frequency is aggregate over all historical data and all selected stores

After uncovering an ancient mystery, Lara Croft embarks on a journey throughout the most treacherous and remote regions of the world to find the secret of immortality. Forming powerful new alliances and relying on her intellect and survival skills, Lara will ultimately embrace her fate as the Tomb Raider.\r\rFeaturing epic, high-octane action moments set in the most beautifully hostile environments on earth, Rise of the Tomb Raider delivers a cinematic survival action adventure where you will join Lara Croft on her first tomb raiding expedition and witness the rise of an icon.\r\rThe Rise of the Tomb Raider: 20 Year Celebration Edition contains:\r\r* Rise of the Tomb Raider game.\r* Limited Edition Artbook & Packaging.\r* \"Blood Ties\" Single Player Story: Explore Lara's childhood home in all-new Story Mode adventure, and uncover a family mystery that will change her life forever.\r* \"Blood Ties\" Nightmare: Lara's worst nightmares come alive as hordes of the undead overrun her childhood home. Compete with friends and create community challenges with card modifiers in an all new Nightmare Mode.\r* Endurance Mode Co-Op: You and a friend must work together to raid tombs in a brutal wilderness. Battle to the top of the leaderboards, as others try to beat your longest survival run.\r* 20 Year Celebration Content: Five classic Lara Croft skins plus a reimagined outfit that pays tribute to Lara's trip to Antarctica from Tomb Raider III. New content also includes the \"Extreme Survivor\" difficulty mode.\r* PlayStation VR-support: Experience \"Blood Ties\" Single Player Story in a whole new way with full Virtual Reality support using the PlayStation VR headset.\r* All DLC Included: Includes all previously released downloadable content, plus new outfits, weapons, and Expedition Cards that will keep you customizing, expanding, and challenging your friends to new adventures.
— Metacritic.com
